Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒錯 就是那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服…繼續…好厲害…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.27,0:01:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.27,0:01:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次PIROTAN你最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.48,0:02:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三階段你發出的絕招光線我完全敵不過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.48,0:02:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去沖澡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.05,0:02:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外還有你…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.22,0:02:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.99,0:02:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是瑪利亞 完工了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.49,0:02:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 就在前面的STAR DUST的306室
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.63,0:02:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛭川先生在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.67,0:02:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次結束後就可以收工了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.47,0:02:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.91,0:02:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事外出…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一條留言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想繼續做這種事到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.92,0:02:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事外出…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.09,0:02:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請在「嗶」的一聲後留下姓名與留言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.14,0:03:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙唇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.88,0:03:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\an8}(90分鐘25000日元)\N(良家女子兼職 新人陸續加入中)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\an8}(為您介紹您喜歡的類型)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有兩條留言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想繼續這種事到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.03,0:03:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連自己是誰都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.53,0:03:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說得自己像受害人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留言播放完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.07,0:03:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰(我是誰)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是晴美 蝶野晴美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我問你 晴美是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴美是我 我就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說謊 那不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.79,0:03:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴美是冒牌貨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說了 我不想和你爭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引起爭吵的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.54,0:04:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你擅自出現的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.61,0:04:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.11,0:04:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是瑪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.11,0:04:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前就在了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.24,0:04:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 那不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從人氣設計師鷺月子遇襲開始的道路魔連續傷人案件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的受害者出現在武藏野南小學裏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「球棒少年」的目的到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.19,0:04:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接二連三的迷團
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.86,0:04:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令附近的居民感到十分恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四名受害者鯛良優一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.57,0:04:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現正在慈愛大學附屬醫院住院
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.74,0:04:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的安危受到人們的關注
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.59,0:04:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真難辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:05:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被訊問過的少年出現於第三次犯罪現場
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這次少年自己更成了受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.63,0:05:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知課長會說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果 似乎跟鷺月子沒什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是無差別襲擊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別隨便下定論
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.17,0:05:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論多麼不可思議的犯罪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也一定有其因果關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次事件 前兩個與月子有關
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.21,0:05:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後兩個與鯛良優一有關
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.22,0:05:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要月子與優一間存在關係的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因果關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一步步來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.27,0:05:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是學校考生們的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.68,0:05:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 和那些放在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.68,0:05:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.78,0:06:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝶野小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.45,0:06:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能給我沏杯茶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常會變得不清楚自己究竟身處何方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的歸宿是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.74,0:06:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是我的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.91,0:06:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是真正的我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟害怕別人而扮樸素的你差得很遠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.15,0:06:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在享受自我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.69,0:06:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 別再隨便用我的手袋了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.16,0:06:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才和瑪利亞談過了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪利亞似乎感覺到逐漸消失的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.67,0:06:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但對消失一事並不感到恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她才說現在正享受自我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪利亞希望你能找到安身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.85,0:07:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你找回自我 瑪利亞也會安心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.59,0:07:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為沒必要完全接受瑪利亞的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.89,0:07:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過她拜託我了 所以我轉告給你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.04,0:07:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留言播放完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.21,0:07:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,課題研究指導的日程表
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.65,0:07:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年好忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為今年的重考生比較多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝶野小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請和我結婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.18,0:08:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留言已刪除
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.31,0:08:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你不做了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 你已經知道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.19,0:08:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我是瑪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.36,0:08:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遺憾 要嫁人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.09,0:08:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.59,0:08:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是感覺是時候退了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我手機號碼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.33,0:08:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知故問
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.13,0:08:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是工作號 我要平時的手機號
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.40,0:08:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 也要和那個身體告別了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.71,0:08:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是我的寄托啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.82,0:08:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有很多好女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚真是最後一次了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.95,0:08:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 父～親～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.57,0:09:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有新的留言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.37,0:09:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.84,0:09:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.71,0:09:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直關在研究室裏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼好的天氣外出
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.25,0:09:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有點不可思議的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.22,0:09:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.39,0:10:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是瑪利亞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.47,0:10:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是「雙唇」的日野
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚能麻煩你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十一點 客戶是蛭川
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.77,0:10:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼知道我的手機號碼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.45,0:10:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？你自己告訴我的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.08,0:10:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.22,0:10:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不做了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.18,0:10:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不做了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.55,0:10:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說過「不決定不做」的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.76,0:10:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天才出來過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.99,0:10:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.46,0:10:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.83,0:10:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一條留言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.09,0:11:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你也太自作主張了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為結婚我就會自動消失啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還把我的東西都收了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.33,0:11:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不原諒你！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.86,0:11:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.68,0:12:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不舉行儀式 只拍結婚照
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.35,0:12:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儀式之類的太麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.58,0:12:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是要留個紀念
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.82,0:12:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近有很多人像你們這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.72,0:12:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會給出目錄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請在裏面挑出三件左右
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本是試穿五件後選出一件的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.67,0:12:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這樣沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.04,0:12:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 啊 可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.38,0:12:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很適合你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.79,0:12:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經一起住了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.59,0:12:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.69,0:12:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後再買房子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.19,0:12:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夠嗆的呢 會有很多事要張羅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:12:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.54,0:13:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人 穿好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.47,0:13:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.75,0:13:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 合身嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.82,0:13:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 到老師的這裏來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會耐心教你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.06,0:13:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會放過你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.69,0:13:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別想自己逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你逃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.23,0:13:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點 清醒過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就沒有瑪利亞 要結婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你傻了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是冒牌貨 趕快消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.88,0:13:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.85,0:13:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在剛才那家店裏買的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.19,0:13:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.96,0:13:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戒指做好之前 請先忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道是在這麼棒的地方 好好舉行一次儀式也不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.64,0:14:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.44,0:14:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請合作一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要連著拍兩張 注意不要閉眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.01,0:14:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 接著再拍一張
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 祝賀你新婚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.26,0:14:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏 還沒有搞戶籍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.50,0:14:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過對方知道你的病嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.34,0:14:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是要向他解釋清楚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.41,0:14:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要在一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.18,0:14:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱瞞下去是很困難的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 對於治療這種病
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.48,0:14:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的協助也是不可缺少的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.42,0:14:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請做好心裏準備
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.43,0:15:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 優一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.96,0:15:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝶野老師你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.83,0:15:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師似乎更需要醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人 還要再等嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.33,0:16:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了 我現在就走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.25,0:16:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪利亞是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.15,0:16:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天那個電話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醉了嗎 那個聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.76,0:16:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人 看來還要等很久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.57,0:16:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 客人你以前坐過我的車嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:17:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只是好像見過你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.57,0:17:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就警告過你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.55,0:17:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢把我的東西全扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.86,0:17:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好心理準備吧 我不會放過你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.86,0:17:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}不會放過你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.16,0:17:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.66,0:17:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 蝶野老師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:17:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝶野老師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.74,0:18:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.91,0:18:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來探病的是我 卻讓你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看上去精神不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.78,0:18:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也似乎比以前更成熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為已經被證明了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.72,0:18:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是兇徒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.06,0:18:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 我是受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.79,0:18:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「球棒少年」令我得到解放
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.10,0:18:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到解放
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吧 我也想得到解放
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就承認了吧 你才是冒牌…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.94,0:18:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白吧 我也想得到解放…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白吧 我也想…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.92,0:18:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.79,0:18:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.56,0:19:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想得到解放
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.36,0:19:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.53,0:19:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.59,0:19:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快承認吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.53,0:19:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是冒牌貨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.52,0:19:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.26,0:20:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.99,0:20:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再叫了 煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.99,0:20:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣死我了 那是什麼態度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.93,0:20:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.51,0:20:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.01,0:20:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的好聽 好好痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.21,0:20:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在把你從痛苦中解放出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.52,0:20:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「球棒少年」解放了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留言已刪除
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.67,0:20:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.54,0:20:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.80,0:20:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.88,0:20:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還不是問口供的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.45,0:21:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先去查她跟鯛良優一的關聯性
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.15,0:21:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她似乎也鬆了口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.59,0:21:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷺月子和川津
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.19,0:21:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鯛良優一 蝶野晴美
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們被道路魔襲擊後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.30,0:21:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎都放下了心頭大石
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.70,0:21:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.64,0:21:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥 小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.07,0:21:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青蛙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.84,0:21:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爺爺 這可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.81,0:21:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能在這裏畫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.11,0:21:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過會兒我給你拿張大紙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.18,0:21:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爺爺 那個是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.39,0:21:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶 蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.93,0:21:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數周內在武藏野多次行兇的道路魔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.33,0:21:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚終於被逮捕了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.77,0:21:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.27,0:21:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}抓住兇徒的是執勤中的平凡巡警
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.77,0:21:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇徒好像被抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.24,0:22:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能講講逮捕兇徒的經過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.02,0:22:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快點的話 又要遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.76,0:22:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小月
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.40,0:22:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.50,0:22:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.14,0:22:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.00,0:24:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢告
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.63,0:24:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金銀聖者的錢之聲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.84,0:24:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽只當作耳邊風
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.37,0:24:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一千零一夜的夢之後七上八下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.58,0:24:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃金狐貍哭了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.92,0:24:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踩高蹺的獅子騎在馬身上
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.39,0:24:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在寬帶網上「啪」地飛馳
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.89,0:24:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.59,0:24:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子漢之路

